<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>케빈아카데미 - 수학 전문 학원</title>
  <meta name="description" content="케빈아카데미 - 1:1 첨삭 지도, 체계적 커리큘럼, 소수정예 수업으로 수학 실력을 키워주는 전문 학원입니다.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css">
</head>
<body class="lp-body">

<!-- ============================================================
     1. Navigation
     ============================================================ -->
<nav class="lp-nav" id="lp-nav">
  <div class="lp-container lp-nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="lp-logo">케빈<span>아카데미</span></a>
    <ul class="lp-nav-links" id="lp-nav-links">
      <li><a href="#features">특징</a></li>
      <li><a href="#curriculum">교육과정</a></li>
      <li><a href="#schedules">시간표</a></li>
      <li><a href="#reviews">후기</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">문의</a></li>
      <li><a href="/management" class="lp-nav-cta">로그인</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="lp-hamburger" id="lp-hamburger" aria-label="메뉴 열기">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ============================================================
     2. Hero
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="lp-hero">
  <div class="lp-container">
    <div class="lp-hero-content">
      <div class="lp-hero-badge">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2z"/></svg>
        수학 전문 학원
      </div>
      <h1>수학의 자신감,<br><em>케빈아카데미</em>에서<br>시작하세요</h1>
      <p class="lp-hero-desc">
        1:1 맞춤 첨삭과 체계적인 커리큘럼으로 학생 개개인의 실력 향상을 이끕니다.
        소수정예 수업으로 빈틈없는 학습 관리를 경험하세요.
      </p>
      <div class="lp-hero-buttons">
        <a href="#contact" class="lp-btn lp-btn-primary">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 01-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 014.11 2h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>
          수강 문의
        </a>
        <a href="/management" class="lp-btn lp-btn-outline">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M15 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-4M10 17l5-5-5-5M15 12H3"/></svg>
          학습 관리 로그인
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-hero-stats">
        <div class="lp-hero-stat">
          <strong>10+</strong>
          <span>년 교육 경력</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-hero-stat">
          <strong>1:1</strong>
          <span>맞춤 첨삭 지도</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-hero-stat">
          <strong>소수정예</strong>
          <span>밀착 관리</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     3. Features
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="lp-section lp-section-gray" id="features">
  <div class="lp-container">
    <div class="lp-section-header">
      <span class="lp-section-label">Why Kevin Academy</span>
      <h2 class="lp-section-title">케빈아카데미가 특별한 이유</h2>
      <p class="lp-section-desc">학생 한 명 한 명에게 맞춘 교육으로 진짜 실력을 키워드립니다</p>
    </div>
    <div class="lp-features-grid">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="lp-feature-card">
        <div class="lp-feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>1:1 첨삭 지도</h3>
        <p>풀이 과정을 꼼꼼히 분석하여 학생의 약점을 정확히 파악하고 개별 피드백을 제공합니다</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="lp-feature-card">
        <div class="lp-feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 17H20"/><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 014 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>체계적 커리큘럼</h3>
        <p>교과 과정에 맞춘 단계별 학습 로드맵으로 빈틈 없이 실력을 쌓아갑니다</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="lp-feature-card">
        <div class="lp-feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>실시간 학습 관리</h3>
        <p>온라인 시스템을 통해 과제 제출, 첨삭 결과, 학습 진도를 실시간으로 확인할 수 있습니다</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="lp-feature-card">
        <div class="lp-feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>소수정예 수업</h3>
        <p>소규모 클래스로 모든 학생이 충분한 관심과 지도를 받을 수 있습니다</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     4. Curriculum
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="lp-section" id="curriculum">
  <div class="lp-container">
    <div class="lp-section-header">
      <span class="lp-section-label">Curriculum</span>
      <h2 class="lp-section-title">교육 과정 안내</h2>
      <p class="lp-section-desc">학년과 목표에 맞는 맞춤형 교육 과정을 운영합니다</p>
    </div>
    <div class="lp-tabs">
      <button class="lp-tab active" data-tab="middle">중등 과정</button>
      <button class="lp-tab" data-tab="high">고등 과정</button>
      <button class="lp-tab" data-tab="exam">내신 대비</button>
    </div>
    <!-- Middle -->
    <div class="lp-tab-panel active" id="tab-middle">
      <div class="lp-curriculum-card">
        <h3>중등 수학 과정</h3>
        <p class="lp-cur-target">대상: 중1 ~ 중3</p>
        <ul class="lp-curriculum-list">
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            수와 연산 기초 다지기
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            방정식·부등식 완벽 정리
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            함수 개념 완성
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            도형·기하 핵심 정리
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            확률과 통계 기초
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            고등 수학 선행 학습
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- High -->
    <div class="lp-tab-panel" id="tab-high">
      <div class="lp-curriculum-card">
        <h3>고등 수학 과정</h3>
        <p class="lp-cur-target">대상: 고1 ~ 고3</p>
        <ul class="lp-curriculum-list">
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            수학 (상)·(하) 체계 정리
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            수학 I·II 심화 학습
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            미적분 완전 정복
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            확률과 통계 고난도
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            기하 집중 과정
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            수능·모의고사 기출 분석
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Exam -->
    <div class="lp-tab-panel" id="tab-exam">
      <div class="lp-curriculum-card">
        <h3>내신 대비 과정</h3>
        <p class="lp-cur-target">대상: 시험 대비가 필요한 모든 학생</p>
        <ul class="lp-curriculum-list">
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            학교별 기출 문제 분석
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            단원별 핵심 개념 정리
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            오답 노트 기반 취약점 보강
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            시험 직전 집중 특강
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            모의 시험 및 실전 연습
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            1:1 약점 맞춤 보충
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     5. Schedules (DB-driven)
     ============================================================ -->
<% if (schedules && schedules.length > 0) { %>
<section class="lp-section lp-section-gray" id="schedules">
  <div class="lp-container">
    <div class="lp-section-header">
      <span class="lp-section-label">Schedules</span>
      <h2 class="lp-section-title">수업 시간표</h2>
      <p class="lp-section-desc">현재 운영 중인 수업 시간표를 확인하세요</p>
    </div>
    <div class="lp-schedules-grid">
      <% schedules.forEach(function(s) {
        let headerData = {};
        try { headerData = typeof s.header_data === 'string' ? JSON.parse(s.header_data) : (s.header_data || {}); } catch(e) {}
        let themeData = {};
        try { themeData = typeof s.theme_data === 'string' ? JSON.parse(s.theme_data) : (s.theme_data || {}); } catch(e) {}
        const subtitle = headerData.subtitle || headerData.programName || '';
      %>
      <a href="/p/<%= s.slug %>" class="lp-schedule-card">
        <div class="lp-schedule-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3><%= s.title %></h3>
        <% if (subtitle) { %><p><%= subtitle %></p><% } %>
        <span class="lp-schedule-link">
          시간표 보기
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        </span>
      </a>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<% } %>

<!-- ============================================================
     6. Reviews
     ============================================================ -->
